      "text": [
        " عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"أَيُّ قَضِيَّةٍ أَعْدَلُ مِنَ اَلْقُرْعَةِ إِذَا فُوِّضَ اَلْأَمْرُ إِلَى اَللَّهِ أَ لَيْسَ اَللَّهُ تَعَالَى يَقُولُ: ۝ فَسٰاهَمَ فَكٰانَ مِنَ اَلْمُدْحَضِينَ ۝ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3391 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"What judgment is more just than the casting of lots (Qur'ah) when the matter is entrusted to Allah (swt)? Does not Allah (swt), the Exalted, say:\n'So they cast lots, and he was among the losers'?\" (Surah As-Saffat 37:141)"
        ]
      }
    },
